            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>很多上班族都会受到腰酸背痛、双腿酸软之苦，放工后又时常做「低头族」看手机萤幕，实在需要在空闲时放松一下。 Theragun 最近推出了 Theragun Pro Plus 及 Relief 按摩枪，让大家可以随时按摩放松身体。</p><h2>Theragun Pro Plus 按摩枪</h2><div class="block-main"><div id="entry-content-1164291" class="entry-content" data-swiftype-name="body" data-swiftype-type="text"><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1223815" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/kan09345-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/kan09345-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/kan09345.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>Theragun Pro Plus 按摩枪使用 USB-C 充电，充满电后最高可使用 150 分钟。用家可控制每分钟震动次数，震幅更达 16mm，有效冲击深层肌肉组织。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1223832" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/kan09369-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/kan09369-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/kan09369.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲用家可控制每分钟震动次数</p><p>Theragun PRO Plus 更具备近红外线 LED 灯 （near infrared LED light） 疗程，通过设置于按摩枪枪头下方手柄内的 13 个 LED 灯，在按摩时同时穿透皮肤照射肌肉组织，促进血液循环和细胞修复，有效增强冲击疗法的恢复效果。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1223829" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/kan09365-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/kan09365-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/kan09365.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲近红外线 LED 灯</p></div><p>下图是振动 （Vibration attachment）、减缓器 （Dampener） 、热疗 （Heated attachment）、楔形 （Wedge）、微点 （Micro-point）及姆指 （Thumb）。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1223833" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/kan09381-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/kan09381-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/kan09381.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲旅行便携袋</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1223818" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/kan09352-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/kan09352-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/kan09352.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p></div><p>热疗为新增设的枪头，可在 10 秒自动升温至 45°C、50 °C、55°C 的 3 种预设温度，配合振动幅度较温和的热疗模式，让用家在运动训练后缓解疼痛及减轻疲劳感。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1223835" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/kan09382-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/kan09382-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/kan09382.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲热疗枪头</p><p>Theragun PRO Plus 手柄以三角型设计，方便无论握住任何位置均可保持平衡。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1223839" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/kan09388-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/kan09388-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/kan09388.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲三角设计</p><p>为方便用家调节振动频率及强度，Theragun PRO Plus 在机身保留 LCD 显示屏及实体操作键，操作数据一目了然。此外，按摩枪亦可通过蓝牙连接 iOS 或 Android 专用手机应用程式，搜寻及下载更多适用的疗程使用。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1223840" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/kan09354-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/kan09354-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/kan09354.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><h2>产品规格</h2><table style="width: 100%; height: 536px;"><tbody><tr style="height: 56px;"><td style="height: 56px;" width="132"><p>体积 / 重量</p></td><td style="height: 56px;"> </td><td style="height: 56px;" width="469"><p>36 x 154 x 65mm / 1.65kg （净机身连内置电池,不包枪头）</p></td><td style="height: 56px;"> </td></tr><tr style="height: 56px;"><td style="height: 56px;" width="132"><p>强度 / 振动频率</p></td><td style="height: 56px;"> </td><td style="height: 56px;" width="469"><p>5 级冲击强度 / 3 种振动频率</p></td><td style="height: 56px;"> </td></tr><tr style="height: 80px;"><td style="height: 80px;" width="132"><p>使用模式</p></td><td style="height: 80px;"> </td><td style="height: 80px;" width="469"><p>冲击治疗、振动治疗、近红外线治疗、热疗、呼吸训练、冷疗（须另购冷疗枪头）</p></td><td style="height: 80px;"> </td></tr><tr style="height: 56px;"><td style="height: 56px;" width="132"><p>使用时间</p></td><td style="height: 56px;"> </td><td style="height: 56px;" width="469"><p>约 150 分钟</p></td><td style="height: 56px;"> </td></tr><tr style="height: 208px;"><td style="height: 208px;" width="132"><p>随盒配备</p></td><td style="height: 208px;"> </td><td style="height: 208px;" width="469"><p>Theragun PRO Plus 按摩枪：</p><p>6 种枪头：标准球 （Standard Ball） 、姆指 （Thumb）、楔形（Wedge）、微点（Micro-point） 、振动 （Vibration attachment）、减缓器 （Dampener）及热疗 （Heated attachment）</p><p>旅行便携袋、USB-C 充电线</p></td><td style="height: 208px;"> </td></tr><tr style="height: 80px;"><td style="height: 80px;" width="132"><p>其他功能</p></td><td style="height: 80px;"> </td><td style="height: 80px;" width="469"><p>生物识别感应器、LCD 显示屏、蓝牙无线传输、连接 iOS 及 Android 专用手机应用程式</p></td></tr></tbody></table><table><tbody><tr><td width="132"><p>建议售价</p></td><td> </td><td width="469"><p style="text-align: left;">HK$4,899</p></td></tr></tbody></table><p></p><h2>Theragun Relief 按摩枪</h2><p>Theragun Relief 同样采用符合人体工学的三角手柄设计，无论用家握著三角形上任何一条手柄，都能保持绝佳平衡，可以更舒适及灵活地按摩身体不同部位。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1223841" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/kan09357-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/kan09357-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/kan09357-rotated.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1223845" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/kan09376-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/kan09376-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/kan09376.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲方便用家按摩不同位置</p><p>按摩枪提供 10mm 振动幅度按摩功能，配合跟机的 3 种按摩枪头： 减缓器 （Dampener） 、标准球 （Standard Ball） 、姆指 （Thumb），可为全身不同肌肉进行按摩，纾缓日常疼痛并改善睡眠质素。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1223842" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/kan09359-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/kan09359-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/kan09359.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>机身配备一个实体键，简单易用。Theragun Relief 仅重 621g，方便随身携带及在出国旅游时使用。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1223843" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/kan09358-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/kan09358-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/kan09358.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲全机身配备一粒按钮，方便易用</p><p>Theragun Relief 机身轻巧和力度适中，特别适合女士使用。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1223844" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/kan09390-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/kan09390-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/kan09390.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><strong>产品规格</strong></p><table><tbody><tr><td width="132"><p>体积 / 重量</p></td><td> </td><td width="469"><p>24.5 x 6.55 x 3.48mm / 621g （净机身连内置电池）</p></td><td> </td></tr><tr><td width="132"><p>使用模式</p></td><td> </td><td width="469"><p>冲击治疗、呼吸训练</p></td><td> </td></tr><tr><td width="132"><p>使用时间</p></td><td> </td><td width="469"><p>约 120 分钟</p></td><td> </td></tr><tr><td width="132"><p>随盒配备</p></td><td> </td><td width="469"><p>Theragun Relief 按摩枪、3 种枪头：减缓器 （Dampener）、标准球（Standard Ball） 、姆指（Thumb）、USB-C 充电线</p></td></tr></tbody></table><table><tbody><tr><td width="132"><p>建议售价</p></td><td> </td><td style="text-align: left;" width="469">HK$1,199</td></tr></tbody></table><h2>总结：热敷头有效缓解肌肉酸痛，三角形手柄方便按摩刁钻角度</h2><p>Theragun Pro Plus 配备多个按摩头中，小编自己最喜欢的就是「热疗」和「微点」。「微点」按摩时可以有效放松绷紧的肌肉，按摩膊头、腰部等位置非常舒服。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1223846" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/kan09397-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/kan09397-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/kan09397.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲微点头</p><p>而「热疗」就可在 10 秒自动升温至 45°C、50 °C、55°C，配合 Theragun Pro Plus 按摩功能就可放松全身肌肉。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1223847" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/kan09382-1-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/kan09382-1-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/kan09382-1.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲热疗头</p><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/03/19/theragun-pro-plus-relief/life-tech/">【实试】Theragun Pro Plus / Relief　发热按摩功能 + 10mm 冲击治疗</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
